⟨vegn der sh-⟩ UNK shokhnte, vos zi iz geshtorbn, vos iz geven dort?

00:22:09.002 --> 00:22:12.539
a! fun di tseyn? yo, zi hot gebetn mayn man nokh,

00:22:12.968 --> 00:22:15.679
er zol,... ir mame iz geshtorbn...

00:22:15.735 --> 00:22:17.636
⟨zol⟩ aroysnemen di tseyn,

00:22:17.760 --> 00:22:21.442
⟨az zi zol zikh⟩ hobn tsu koyfn epes tsu esn, UNK geyn farkoyfn,

00:22:21.442 --> 00:22:23.072
