ven iz geven di ⟨LIBERARE⟩, gedenkt? vos iz...

00:22:54.582 --> 00:22:59.102
m'hot undz ar⟨oy-⟩ m'iz gekumen, m'hot gezogt, ze'mir liberirt, zol'mir geyn, tsu hoyze.

00:22:59.205 --> 00:23:00.161
azoy?

00:22:59.965 --> 00:23:00.819
azoy.

