00:23:03.694 --> 00:23:07.552
m'iz gekumen funem, der ⟨PRIMAR⟩, ikh veys ver er iz dort.

00:23:07.812 --> 00:23:12.041
gekumen zogn, az s'iz geven a, fun zey epes,

00:23:12.115 --> 00:23:15.163
vos m'hot zey geshikt az me zol aroys-, -gibn di yidn,

00:23:15.507 --> 00:23:17.040
zoln zikh geyn.

00:23:16.823 --> 00:23:21.136
vos hot ir geton in yener minut? vi azoy hot ir, vi azoy hot ir gefilt in yener minut?

00:23:20.755 --> 00:23:23.719
vos zol men filn? me geyt. far freyd geyt men

00:23:23.978 --> 00:23:29.530
tsu hoyze. ober ikh bin gekumen aheym, iz ge- nisht geven gornit. kh'hob nit gehat vu tsu arayntsugeyn.

00:23:29.530 --> 00:23:30.604
far vos?

00:23:30.340 --> 00:23:32.679
far vos? vayl di goyim hobn tsevarfn.

00:23:34.069 --> 00:23:35.936
UNK ⟨gegibn⟩ fayer.

00:23:35.976 --> 00:23:37.809
AZ vu zent ir gegan?

00:23:37.933 --> 00:23:39.415
ze'mir gegan.

00:23:39.722 --> 00:23:41.977
vu s'iz geven ergets a,

00:23:42.321 --> 00:23:45.690
a shtelkhl, a vos, iz men arayngegan zitsn.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:48.002
un dernokh dem, vu zent ir ge-...

00:23:47.518 --> 00:23:51.299
un dernokh iz, mayn man iz geven a rumenisher, hot

00:23:51.299 --> 00:23:53.578
zayn mishpokhe aribergeshikt

00:23:53.813 --> 00:23:56.578
a mentshn, er zol undz brengen.

00:23:57.627 --> 00:23:59.378
ze'mir aribergegan. m'hot,

00:23:59.378 --> 00:24:01.670
di barke funem Prut,

00:24:01.778 --> 00:24:05.687
m'hot undz arayngezetst un m'hot undz aribergefirt fun yener zayt.

00:24:06.317 --> 00:24:07.897
un di,

00:24:08.865 --> 00:24:13.598
fun yener zayt, un s'iz geven eyner mit a vogn. mir ho'mir zikh arayngezetst, ⟨er hot undz⟩ tsugefirt.

00:24:13.168 --> 00:24:14.832
vu? voser a shtot?

00:24:14.687 --> 00:24:16.094
