yo, ven...

00:24:30.111 --> 00:24:31.033
yo.

00:24:31.242 --> 00:24:32.991
⟨kh'hob⟩ gemakht.

00:24:31.343 --> 00:24:33.615
un vifl tsayt zent ir geven in Daraban?

00:24:33.958 --> 00:24:35.444
tsvontsik yor.

00:24:35.713 --> 00:24:37.496
vos hot ir geton dortn?

00:24:37.232 --> 00:24:40.188
mayn man hot geton; ikh hob ni-...

00:24:38.785 --> 00:24:40.112
vos hot er gemakht?

00:24:40.354 --> 00:24:41.895
er iz geven a shnayder.

00:24:41.895 --> 00:24:44.154
hot ⟨men⟩ rakhmones gehat; m'hot im gebrakht

00:24:44.154 --> 00:24:46.018
hoyzns farrikhtn.

00:24:46.041 --> 00:24:48.470
m'hot shoyn gut gelebt dort dam⟨ls⟩?

00:24:46.058 --> 00:24:47.014
⟨vos zhe hobn⟩...

00:24:48.505 --> 00:24:49.832
m'hot shoyn gut gelebt?

00:24:49.931 --> 00:24:53.795
⟨⟩, nisht gut, ⟨nu⟩, ikh bin dokh a fremde geven.

00:24:56.487 --> 00:24:59.096
un di kinder, vu zenen zey geboyrn gevorn?

00:25:00.081 --> 00:25:01.374
Rumenye.

00:25:01.802 --> 00:25:03.230
voser a plats?

00:25:03.220 --> 00:25:04.598
Daraban.

00:25:05.127 --> 00:25:06.454
hob ikh gemakht zey.

00:25:06.088 --> 00:25:07.331
tsvey kinder?

00:25:07.084 --> 00:25:08.581
tsvey kinder.

00:25:08.485 --> 00:25:11.060
un dernokh dem zent ir gekumen in land?

00:25:10.830 --> 00:25:13.051
yo. hot men gezogt, s'iz a,

00:25:13.075 --> 00:25:17.338
 m'hot rekht baytsuleygn aktn, me zol forn keyn Yisroel.

00:25:17.428 --> 00:25:18.266
yo.

00:25:18.390 --> 00:25:20.470
ho'mir baygeleygt un m'iz geforn.

00:25:20.938 --> 00:25:23.699
un vi azoy iz geven in land ven ⟨zen⟩t, ir zent gekumen?

00:25:24.128 --> 00:25:28.709
