00:25:28.837 --> 00:25:31.760
der man iz aheymgekumen nokh fun di daytshn krank,

00:25:32.245 --> 00:25:37.564
mit ⟨eyn nir⟩, mit, a, di kishke aroysgelozt in UNK.

00:25:37.797 --> 00:25:39.310
ir hot gearbet do?

00:25:39.332 --> 00:25:40.581
ver, ikh?

00:25:39.923 --> 00:25:40.811
yo.

00:25:40.885 --> 00:25:44.564
