00:26:00.544 --> 00:26:02.343
un di kinder hobn gelernt?

00:26:02.333 --> 00:26:04.376
yo, kinder hobn gelernt.

00:26:04.341 --> 00:26:06.613
⟨,⟩ gehat nakhes fun di kinder.

00:26:07.227 --> 00:26:10.419
